{"tid":1180261,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三輪版「Gogoro」強勢來襲 Sway 主打騎車「雙腳不落地」","createTime":"2019-05-31T16:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T13:56:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a05ffa2a33a3b4fe39b98daa8b0c1ae21c6cd7","tid":1180261,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.bnextmedia.com.tw/img/3x2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.bnextmedia.com.tw%2Fimg%2F3x2.png&h=39d0a76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通工具綠色革命，已經在全球許多大都市颳起旋風，尤其是電動機車創新這塊領域，大陸有小牛電動車，台灣有Gogoro挑戰傳統二輪機車商機，陸續在銷售端開出好成績。但這一次來自美國的新創公司，打算推出「三輪」電動機車，號稱續航力也有近百公里，要用獨特的騎乘感受吸引消費者。<br />\n<br />\n沒看錯，前方兩顆輪胎轉彎時，同時傾斜大幅度，卻能夠維持穩定。這款Sway三輪電動機車，<span style=\"color: red;\">靠著專利技術，主打騎乘「免放腳」，連創辦人家裡的60歲老奶奶都能騎</span>。比起汽車大廠Toyota研發的i-Road，也更加貼近摩托車外型。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消費者最擔心的續航力，Sway提供跟Gogoro相去不遠的內容，以時速48公里情況下，能騎乘64公里；Plus版本能騎更遠，接近100公里，甚至最高時速，能衝到88公里，一般都會區使用，並沒有太大問題。<br />\n<br />\n比較特別的地方，在於Sway不走「交換電池」路線，跟小牛電動車一樣，都選擇「家用充電」方便使用。一般110伏特到240伏特都可以直接充電。只要喜歡，也能付費升級在家裡裝設快速充電站！<br />\n<br />\nSway的性能相當具有競爭力，為了大幅量產，也找了歐洲品牌Govecs合作，期待雙方一起在電動機車領域攜手抗敵。但目前看來最大問題會落在「價格」，最便宜版本要24萬新台幣（7500美元），高速的Plus版更得花36萬新台幣才能入手，就算想買還得先墊墊荷包。"},{"pid":"c94fc94e4513196447386794c04d639a4a97f5f5","tid":1180261,"uid":205734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"47774aa9dfd25d691c6c1a6e8578f290eafa672e","tid":1180261,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0E8QPEWQhJ0/Vz9RZOsPl8I/AAAAAAACeu0/FaLMgWfvMcMtUXn20Y71CQYohMCgg9d_wCKgB/s600/%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%259C%2596%25E4%25BA%258C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-0E8QPEWQhJ0%2FVz9RZOsPl8I%2FAAAAAAACeu0%2FFaLMgWfvMcMtUXn20Y71CQYohMCgg9d_wCKgB%2Fs600%2F%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E5%25259C%252596%2525E4%2525BA%25258C.png&h=5fa7ed8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"985d583faec5969601b0d0556f44c6d1a84e51e7","tid":1180261,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/px/article/39653/BN-2016-05-20-221506-77\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Fpx%2Farticle%2F39653%2FBN-2016-05-20-221506-77&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=a8fbf515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/px/article/39653/BN-2016-05-20-221506-77</a>"},{"pid":"68d75be5eb448eb8bd70abcf61461646a2ceee02","tid":1180261,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"香港？咪又係犯法"},{"pid":"0caf64cb0b19e53d519245f5bb410b3f2403e8af","tid":1180261,"uid":247323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69fe79ebd80de4c02328d4252ad31572fce52c9f","tid":1180261,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}